
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I select 'Flow measurement' from 'Examination technique' dropdown menu in Page 03 - Sequences of Cardio MRI
And	I'm on Page 04 of Cardio MRI
When I select the radio button 'Finding'
Then 'Measured values' tab is active and selected by default
And 'Aorta ascendens' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pulmonary artery' checkbox is enabled
And 'Mitral valve' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Aorta ascendens' checkbox
Then 'Max. flow' input field is enabled
And 'Min. flow' input field is enabled
And 'Positive flow' input field is enabled
And 'Negative flow' input field is enabled
And 'Regurgitant fraction' input field is enabled
And 'Reference image flow curve' upload box is enabled
And 'Reference image PC measuring' upload box is enabled

When I select 'Pulmonary artery' checkbox
Then 'Max. flow' input field is enabled
And 'Min. flow' input field is enabled
And 'Positive flow' input field is enabled
And 'Negative flow' input field is enabled
And 'Regurgitant fraction' input field is enabled
And 'Reference image flow curve' upload box is enabled
And 'Reference image PC measuring' upload box is enabled

When I select 'Mitral valve' checkbox
Then 'Max. flow' input field is enabled
And 'Min. flow' input field is enabled
And 'Positive flow' input field is enabled
And 'Negative flow' input field is enabled
And 'Regurgitant fraction' input field is enabled
And 'Reference image flow curve' upload box is enabled
And 'Reference image PC measuring' upload box is enabled